{"word":"Ater","slug":"ater","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ater</b> <a href=\"#/H333\">H333</a> <br/> 1. A descendant of Hezekiah, who returned from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=16'>Ezr 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=21'>Neh 7:21</a><br/> 2. A porter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=42'>Ezr 2:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=45'>Neh 7:45</a><br/> 3. An Israelite, who subscribed to Nehemiah's covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=17'>Neh 10:17</a>"}]}